Justin Piszcz wrote:
> Why are there only 7-8 loop devices available?
> What options do I have if I want to mount, say, 100 isos?
Documentation/kernel-parameters.txt say:
max_loop=       [LOOP] Maximum number of loopback devices that can
		be mounted
		Format: <1-256>
